query: SELECT T1.Club_ID, T2.Team_Leader FROM club_leader AS T1 INNER JOIN club AS T2 ON T1.Club_ID = T2.Club_ID WHERE T1.Member_ID = 68 GROUP BY T2.Team_Leader ORDER BY T2.Team_Leader DESC;
question: What are the clubs led by each team leader for member 68, listed in descending order by team leader?

query: SELECT MAX(T2.Age), T2.Member_ID, T3.Member_ID, T3.Club_ID FROM member AS T2 JOIN club AS T1 JOIN club_leader AS T3 ON T3.Member_ID = T2.Member_ID AND T1.Club_ID = T3.Club_ID WHERE T3.Club_ID IN (SELECT Club_ID FROM club AS g WHERE g.Club_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR g.Club_ID > 43 LIMIT 6) GROUP BY T3.Member_ID, T3.Club_ID HAVING MAX(T3.Club_ID) < 78

query: SELECT MAX(T1.Age), T1.Name FROM member AS T1 JOIN club_leader AS T2 ON T2.Member_ID = T1.Member_ID WHERE T1.Member_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 GROUP BY T1.Name ORDER BY T1.Name DESC LIMIT 3;
question: What are the names and maximum ages of the three oldest members with member IDs between 1 and 10, ordered alphabetically by name in descending order?
